peter j solomon company  wikipedia peter j solomon company from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search peter j solomon company type private company industry investment banking founded  headquarters  avenue of the americas new york city united states number of employees  website wwwpjsccom peter j solomon company pjsc is an investment banking advisory firm pjsc advises clients on mergers acquisitions divestitures restructurings recapitalizations private placements and corporate strategy the firm also provides counsel to corporate boards renders fairness opinions and has built a successful practice defending companies in proxy and takeover contests the firm’s practices cover a broad range of industry verticals including retail ecommerce and distribution food retail and restaurants energy technology media and telecommunications healthcare and real estate landmark transactions have included advising harrahs in its  billion sale to apollo global management and texas pacific group advising may stores in its  billion sale to federated department stores advising phillipsvan heusen in its  billion acquisition of tommy hilfiger corporation and advising the board of directors of apparel and footwear conglomerate jones group inc on its sale to private equity firm sycamore partners among its current advisory assignments pjsc is representing cbs outdoor american apparel overseas shipholding group radioshack and energy future holdingstxu recent crossborder advisory work includes representation of the london stock exchange group lseg on its pending  billion acquisition of frank russell company this acquisition marks the second of two transactions that pjsc has executed for lseg in  pjsc represented lseg specifically its subsidiary ftse group on the formation of a joint venture with tmx datalinx creating the third largest fixed income etf index provider in the world pjsc’s advisory assignments in  included office depots  billion merger with officemax and under armours  million acquisition of digital fitness technology company mapmyfitness noteworthy  and  assignments included ebay in its acquisition of gsi commerce sony in its acquisition of emi music publishing zagat survey in its sale to google walgreen company in its acquisition of certain assets from bioscrip inc cost plus inc in its sale to bed bath  beyond chico’s in its acquisition of boston proper jc penney in its investment in martha stewart living omnimedia media general in the sale of most of its newspapers to berkshire hathaway phillipsvan heusen corps  billion acquisition of warnaco group ppr in its  million sale of onestopplus group and mckesson corporations  billion acquisition of pss world medical inc contents  business divisions  history  references  external links business divisionsedit investment banking • corporate advisory • restructuring advisory • private placements historyedit pjsc was founded in  by peter j solomon and was the first private independent investment banking firm on wall street created to mirror the ethos and culture of the original privately held investment banks at a time when many of the large investment banks had gone public in the ensuing decades the firm has grown to more than  people and has added senior bankers drawn from major wall street investment banks in june  pjsc entered into an alliance with natixis the international corporate investment insurance and financial services arm of groupe bpce frances second largest financial institution  selling a  stake in the firm the remaining  of pjscs ownership continues to be held by its existing partners the natixis investment is intended to create an enhanced global ma advisory and financing platform coupling pjscs entrepreneurial spirit with a multifaceted debt and equity financing vehicle that offers international reach across the americas emea and asia solomon is a former vice chairman of lehman brothers where he was cochairman of investment banking from  to  mr solomon served as deputy mayor of economic policy and development in new york city under mayor edward koch and in  he served as counselor to the united states treasury in the carter administration in  he testified before the financial crisis inquiry commission created by the us congress referencesedit  with gsi deal ebay shifts to big retail the new york times march     its official sonyled group purchases emi music publishing for  billion billboard november     in a twist google reviews zagat and decides to bite the new york times september     walgreens to acquire bioscrips community specialty pharmacies and centralized specialty and mail service pharmacy businesses reuters february     bed bath  beyond to buy cost plus the new york times may     chicos fas to acquire boston proper reuters august     penney ceo calls martha stewart deal a centerpiece reuters december     berkshire bets again on newspapers with media general deal the new york times may     ward  pp   wall street back to the old school financial times july     a b dreamteam investment banking as old wall street crumbles industry veteran peter j solomon snaps up a few of its superstars cnn money march     kanter stein and jick  pp   financial crisis inquiry commission the financial crisis inquiry report pdf retrieved   external linksedit peter j solomon company company website retail restructuring seen ahead womens wear daily april   via the pjsc website pj solomons new restructuring head counsels bankruptcy avoidance wall street journal november   ward vicky  the devils casino friendship betrayal and the high stakes games played inside lehman brothers hoboken nj john wiley  sons isbn   peter solomon hires new media team head the new york times february   kanter rosabeth moss barry a stein and todd d jick  challenge of organizational change how companies experience it and leaders guide it  new york simon  schuster isbn  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlepeterjsolomoncompanyoldid categories investment bank