ing • corporate advisory • restructuring advisory • private placements historyedit pjsc was founded in  by peter j solomon and was the first private independent investment banking firm on wall street created to mirror the ethos and culture of the original privately held investment banks at a time when many of the large investment banks had gone public in the ensuing decades the firm has grown to more than  people and has added senior bankers drawn from major wall street investment banks in june  pjsc entered into an alliance with natixis the international corporate investment insurance and financial services arm of groupe bpce frances second largest financial institution  selling a  stake in the firm the remaining  of pjscs ownership continues to be held by its existing partners the natixis investment is intended to create an enhanced global ma advisory and financing platform coupling pjscs entrepreneurial spirit with a multifaceted debt and equity financing vehicle that offers international reach across the americas emea and asia solomon is a former vice chairman of lehman brothers where he was cochairman of investment banking from  to  mr solomon served as deputy mayor of economic policy and development in new york city under mayor edward koch and in  he served as counselor to the united states treasury in the carter administration in  he testified before the financial crisis inquiry commission created by the us congress referencesedit  with gsi deal ebay shifts to big retail the new york times march     its official sonyled group purchases emi music publishing for  billion billboard november     in a twist google reviews zagat and decides to bite the new york times september     walgreens to acquire bioscrips community specialty pharmacies and centralized specialty and mail service pharmacy businesses reuters february     bed bath  beyond to buy cost plus the new york times may     chicos fas to acquire boston proper reuters august     penney ceo calls martha ste