 acquisitions sales restructurings recapitalizations capital markets solutions and activism defense across a range of industries including retail media and entertainment infrastructure and energy our difference is that we offer unmatched industry knowledge in the sectors we cover going deep into those sectors to provide the most comprehensive strategic solutions tailored to generate longterm shareholder value we are the best of all worlds today peter j solomon company is an independentlyrun affiliate of natixis part of groupe bpce a top ten european and top  global bank as such our clients enjoy proprietary access to an international advisory and financing platform with coverage throughout north and south america emea and asia practice areas mergers  acquisitionsma is at the core of pjsc’s advisory services we partner with clients to stimulate creative strategic solutions restructuring  recapitalizationwe have led some of the largest and most complex restructuring transactions over the past  years special committee  fairness opinion practicewe bring an independent voice to special committees and board of directors on a wide range of transactions financing advisoryfree from conflicts we advise clients in accessing the public capital markets as well as highly tailored bespoke capital from specialty lenders hedge funds and other institutional investors activist defensewe advise management teams and boards of directors on their vulnerability to and defense from shareholder activism and unsolicited or hostile takeover bids industry expertise global retailwith a deep heritage in the retailing industry our unique crosssector approach and creative strategies help to generate longterm shareholder value food retail  restaurantsour team provides investment banking advisory services to clients across various food retail and restaurant subsectors ecommerce  retail technologypjsc has one of the largest senior banking teams dedicated to advising clients on how they engage with and