o assume increasing levels of responsibility commensurate with their progress as a result pjsc believes our professionals develop important client and deal experience earlier than their peers at larger more structured investment banking firms if you are resourceful energetic and demonstrate initiative you can build a career at pjsc we regularly promote our junior bankers up through the ranks people who have demonstrated leadership skills who can flourish in a team environment and who are flexible by nature and creative in their thinking will thrive at our firm we recruit the best and brightest this is what we look for in candidates » leadership skills » highly motivated » team players » strong analytical  quantitative skills » strong communication skills » creative thinking peter j solomon company is ranked  in the vault guide to the top  banking employers read the vault review pjsc culture pjsc’s culture is built on honesty integrity and a collective commitment to providing clients with sound unbiased advice we are guided on a daily basis by these values and pursue them in a collaborative environment that promotes excellence and creativity intellectual integrity clients retain pjsc to render objective conclusions about strategic decisions which affect their capitalizations our advice is free from conflicts of interest the partnership does not invest for its own account trade securities provide research or manage client assets relationship focused our personal responsive approach emphasizes relationships not transactions and is at the heart of our concept of investment banking a dedicated team remains with the client throughout every project we give back we encourage and support our people to engage in the nonprofit world whether through volunteer projects participation in charitable events or donating their time in nonprofit board positions the level of access to senior bankers as a summer intern is unparalleled — vault guide to the top  investment banking employers  edition mentors are fantastic and genuinely helpful people listen to your aspirations and make a legitimate effort to help you — vault guide to the top  investment banking employers  edition collegial atmosphere where colleagues know each other well and pull together on transactions — vault guide to the top  investment banking employers  edition we look for the best candidates that are capable motivated and willing to put forth the effort needed to provide excellent service to our clients — vault guide to the top  investment banking employers  edition see our people join our team analyst in this entry level position you will work in small deal teams with two or more senior members of the firm performing among other things financial modeling and valuation analyses analysts work closely with clients read more associate associates are usually experienced professionals typically with mba’s they work in small client project teams led by a managing director to analyze and execute various transactions read more summer internship summer internships for analyst and associate positions give you the opportunity to see what investment banking is all about it is a  week commitment where you are expected to be a valuable team member right from the start summer analysts and associates have daytoday contact with senior professionals and clients read more financial consulting  yahoo local search results sign inhomenewsmailfinancetumblrweathersportsmessengersettings weblocalimagescategory taxes car insurance home insurance financial consulting accounting  bookkeeping banks insurance financial services life insurance personal financing commercial insurance investment brokerages commercial banks financial planning real estate financing management  consulting automotive financing atms payroll investment services health insurance investment banks cash  check advances business services credit  debt services real estate agents corporate accounting law firms consumer services restaurant