ion from  to  mr solomon was deputy mayor of economic policy and development in new york city under mayor edward i koch he was also chairman of the new york city health and hospitals corporation which operated  municipal hospitals he served as counselor to the united states treasury in the carter administration in  in  mr solomon served as cochairman of new york governor andrew m cuomo’s tax reform and fairness commission charged with proposing reforms to the state’s complex tax code  he also served on governor cuomo’s spending and government efficiency commission sage mr solomon writes frequently about public policy issues professional affiliations director monro mufflerbrake inc previous professional affiliations director associated dry goods corporation director bkf capital group inc director centennial cellular corporation director century communications corp director esquire inc director general cigar holdings director lin broadcasting corporation director office depot inc director phillipsvan heusen corporation director the stop  shop companies inc director zagat survey llc nonforprofit affiliations member boards of managers memorial sloankettering cancer center memorial hospital for cancer and allied diseases and sloankettering institute for cancer research trustee american museum of natural history cochairman american friends musée d’orsay member of the board of governors of the alzheimer’s drug discovery foundation director and chairman emeritus the manhattan theatre club chairman friends of the center for jewish studies – harvard university trustee lucius littauer foundation trustee the federation of jewish philanthropies of new york city academic credentials mr solomon received his ba cum laude from harvard college and his mba from harvard business school back to our people real estate contact us contact us real estate our advisory approach think like an owner drawing upon more than  years of experience and as a complement to our legacy advisory services pjsc offers clients a suite of services dedicated exclusively to maximizing their real estate assets whereas many firms in advising real estate do so only as intermediaries pjsc advises from the unique position of having been principals and owners of real estate as a result we are able to analyze opportunities from our clients’ perspective pjscs partnership with joss realty partners in its mm pjscjoss real estate fund has produced a unique set of tools when it comes to representing clients helping clients derive value from real estate we understand that optimizing real estate is not just about maximizing real estate value but also involves strategy to have the real estate maximize the value of the business our professionals bring together a wealth of knowledge and creativity to address the real estate assets of a company we position and monetize them as efficiently as possible and determine the best course of action for a company’s portfolio the real estate markets a changing tide over the last  years there has been a seminal change in how real estate is valued and financed real estate is now considered a valuable long term asset that can be efficiently financed and capitalized as a result of this change many companies whose real estate holdings up until recently simply sat on balance sheets are able to rethink these assets and extract significant value from them the maturity and breadth of today’s landscape offers more capital sources than ever before which translates to more options for companies this enables pjsc to present multiple options for a real estate transaction whether it be stand alone or as part of a corporate financing or ma assignment overview of the us real estate market pdf recent advisory work select recent transactions include advising a new york city family office on the valuation and partial sale of a mm portfolio of downtown new york city office buildings and producing a valuation study for a forprofit postsecondary institution visàvis its mm 