arding the total amount of consideration that was paid in connection with the az transaction and thus regarding the fee owed to plaintiffs under the agreement the court denies the plaintiffs summary judgment motion to the extent it seeks an award of damages the parties are directed to use their best efforts to resolve the damages issue the trial of this action will be limited to the issue of damages the final pretrial conference is hereby adjourned to june   at  am and the parties are directed to consult and make submissions in advance of the conference as provided in the pretrial scheduling order docket entry no  this memorandum opinion and order resolves docket entry numbers  and  as further set forth in this order signed by judge laura taylor swain on  spo entered   notice of conference a telephone conference in this matter has been scheduled for april   at  pm plaintiffs counsel shall initiate the call by placing a conference call to chambers at   any request for an adjournment must be made to the court in writing at least two business days prior to the conference telephone conference set for  at  pm before magistrate judge frank maas cf entered   motion for reconsideration  document filed by adc products uk limitedschissel michael entered   memorandum of law in support re  motion for reconsideration   document filed by adc products uk limited schissel michael entered   memorandum of law in opposition re  motion for reconsideration   document filed by peter j solomon company lp peter j solomon securities company llc berns mitchell entered   notice of conference a settlement conference in this matter has been scheduled for may   at  pm the conference shall take place in courtroom a of the daniel patrick moynihan united states courthouse  pearl street new york new york counsel are reminded to comply with judge maas individual settlement procedures which are available on his page of the courts website requests for adjournment must be made to the court in writing at